{"tid":473208,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【日本科技】億計蟑螂獲「飼養」吃廚餘剩食　死後磨成粉餵雞","createTime":"2017-11-19T04:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T04:33:42.000Z","uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"936899aa51ccf378372c1219244ad179118951c9","tid":473208,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:29:59.000Z","msg":"廚餘和剩食等問題近年愈來愈多港人關注，上任特首梁振英的夫人唐青儀，也曾創辦過相關慈善組織。<br />\n<br />\n有日本傳媒報道，日本岐阜縣的高山市餐廚垃圾處理中心，每天約會將全市收集到的14、5噸各式回收到的剩菜剩飯，送入一個「飼養車間」，內裏「飼養」着美洲蟑螂，牠們每天可以吃掉比自己體重還多5%的廚餘剩食。整個飼養車間，最多可容納3億隻美洲蟑螂。<br />\n<br />\n更重要的是，據中心展示的農業部檢測中心報告，這些負責吃廚餘剩食的美洲蟑螂，未檢驗出有沙門氏菌及大腸桿菌等有害物質，卻有高達71.2%的粗蛋白質，蛋白質含量比外國進口的秘魯魚粉等還高。故此，當這些美洲蟑螂死了之後，就都被磨成飼料來養雞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/19/122845_ec106a8d23dffa7adc9ab6c2392bf28e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2F122845_ec106a8d23dffa7adc9ab6c2392bf28e.jpg&h=7ac605c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n短片：<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.miaopai.com/show/channel/4mNrg38AP-NaPAzq9YDqVi3yZNtqMgTnO~FACA__\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.miaopai.com%2Fshow%2Fchannel%2F4mNrg38AP-NaPAzq9YDqVi3yZNtqMgTnO~FACA__&d=xUcJZgEr%2B061WxnRHYnldPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=16d98e18\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.miaopai.com/show/channel/4mNrg38AP-NaPAzq9YDqVi3yZNtqMgTnO~FACA__</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171118/s00004/1510996752833\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171118%2Fs00004%2F1510996752833&d=xUcJZgEr%2B061WxnRHYnldPM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=2340858a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171118%2Fs00004%2F1510996752833&h=85191faf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171118/s00004/1510996752833</a>"},{"pid":"06661d91d005dd